Package com.tapjoy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TJActionRequest
    Interface definition for a request of action to be performed.
    TJAwardCurrencyListener
    Any class calling Tapjoy.awardCurrency(int, TJAwardCurrencyListener) should implement TJAwardCurrencyListener so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/balance info.
    TJConnectListener
    Any class calling com.tapjoy.Tapjoy#connect(android.content.Context, java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.util.Hashtable, TJConnectListener) should implement this class so it can receive the callback on whether the connect call is successful or not.
    TJEarnedCurrencyListener
    Listener to inform the app whenever virtual currency has been earned.
    TJGetCurrencyBalanceListener
    Any class calling Tapjoy.getCurrencyBalance(TJGetCurrencyBalanceListener) should implement TJGetCurrencyBalanceListener so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/balance info.
    TJOffersListener
    Listener class which sends callbacks whenever receiving a response to Tapjoy.showOffers(TJOffersListener).
    TJPlacementListener  
    TJSpendCurrencyListener
    Any class calling Tapjoy.spendCurrency(int, TJSpendCurrencyListener) should implement TJSpendCurrencyListener so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/balance info.
    TJVideoListener  
    TJViewListener
    Callback methods which get triggered whenever a Tapjoy view opens or closes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Tapjoy
    Created by Tapjoy.
    TapjoyConnectFlag
    Flags used in Tapjoy#connect(android.content.Context, String, String, java.util.Hashtable) to define special startup options.
    TapjoyLog
    This class is used to control debug messages to the console for Tapjoy SDK related classes.
    TapjoyVideoStatus
    Status codes used in the callbacks videos.
    TJPlacement
